lar Prakashan\n|  location =Mumbai\n| isbn =81-7154-708-7\n| year =1993\n|postscript=<!--None-->}}.\n* {{Citation\n| last =Meredith\n| first =George\n| title =Bhagwan: The Most Godless Yet the Most Godly Man\n| publisher =Rebel Publishing House\n| year =1988\n| location =Pune\n|postscript=<!--None-->}}.\n* {{Citation\n| last =Milne\n| first =Hugh\n| title =Bhagwan: The God That Failed\n| publisher =Caliban Books\n| year =1986\n| location =London\n| isbn =1-85066-006-9\n|postscript=<!--None-->}}.\n* {{Citation\n| last =Mistlberger\n| first =P.T.\n| title =The Three Dangerous Magi: Osho, Gurdjieff, Crowley\n| publisher =O Books\n| pages = 713\n| url = https://books.google.com/?id=C6nUWy4UYocC&printsec=frontcover#v=onepage&q&f=false\n| isbn =978-1-84694-435-2\n| year =2010\n|accessdate=12 July 2011}}.\n* {{Citation\n| last =Mullan\n| first =Bob\n| title =Life as Laughter: Following Bhagwan Shree Rajneesh\n| publisher =[[Routledge]] & Kegan Paul Books Ltd\n|  location =London, Boston, Melbourne and Henley\n| isbn =0-7102-0043-9\n| year =1983\n|postscript=<!--None-->}}.\n* {{Citation\n| last =Osho\n| title =Autobiography of a Spiritually Incorrect Mystic\n| publisher =[[St. Martin's Press|St. Martin's Griffin]]\n| year =2000\n| location =New York, NY\n| isbn =0-312-25457-1\n|postscript=<!--None-->}}.\n* {{Citation\n| last =Bhagwan Shree Rajneesh\n| title =Glimpses of a Golden Childhood\n| publisher =Rajneesh Foundation International\n|  location =Rajneeshpuram\n| isbn =0-88050-715-2\n| year =1985\n|postscript=<!--None-->}}.\n* {{Citation\n| last =Osho\n| title =Meditation: the first and last freedom\n| publisher =St. Martin's Griffin\n| isbn =978-0-312-33663-9\n| year =2004\n|postscript=<!--None-->}}.\n* {{Citation | last =Palmer | first =Susan J. | author-link =Susan J. Palmer | title = Charisma and Abdication: A Study of the Leadership of Bhagwan Shree Rajneesh | journal = Sociological Analysis | volume =49 | issue =2 | pages =119\u2013135 | year =1988 | doi = 10.2307/3711009|postscript=<!--None-->| jstor =3711009 | url =https://semanticscholar.org/paper/9bd7f23a7df6eab01adac25e0e1609e6eb9c0150 }}, reprinted in {{harvnb|Aveling|1999|pp=363\u2013394}}.\n* {{Citation\n| last = Palmer\n| first =Susan J.\n| author-link =Susan J. Palmer\n| last2 =Sharma\n| first2=Arvind (eds.)\n| title =The Rajneesh Papers: Studies in a New Religious Movement\n| publisher =[[Motilal Banarsidass]]\n|  location =Delhi\n| isbn =81-208-1080-5\n| year = 1993\n|postscript=<!--None-->}}.\n* {{Citation\n| last = Prasad\n| first =Ram Chandra\n| title =Rajneesh: The Mystic of Feeling\n| publisher =[[Motilal Banarsidass]]\n| year =1978\n| location =Delhi\n| isbn = 0-89684-023-9\n|postscript=<!--None-->}}.\n* {{Citation\n |last=Sam\n |title=Life of Osho\n |publisher=Sannyas\n |year=1997\n |location=London\n |url=http://www.enlightenedbeings.com/pdf/life_of_osho.pdf\n |accessdate=12 July 2011\n |url-status=unfit\n |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120321124111/http://www.enlightenedbeings.com/pdf/life_of_osho.pdf\n |archivedate=21 March 2012\n}}.\n* {{Citation\n| last =Shunyo\n| first =Ma Prem\n| title =My Diamond Days with Osho: The New Diamond Sutra\n| publisher =[[Motilal Banarsidass]]\n|  location =Delhi\n| isbn =81-208-1111-9\n| year =1993\n|postscript=<!--None-->}}.\n* {{Citation\n| last =Sloterdijk\n| first =Peter\n| author-link = Peter Sloterdijk\n| title =Selbstversuch: Ein Gespr\u00e4ch mit Carlos Oliveira\n| publisher =Carl Hanser Verlag\n|  location =M\u00fcnchen, Wien\n| isbn =3-446-18769-3\n| year =1996\n|postscript=<!--None-->|language=de}}.\n* {{Citation\n| last =Storr\n| first =Anthony\n| author-link =Anthony Storr\n| title =Feet of Clay&nbsp;\u2013 A Study of Gurus\n| publisher =[[Harper Collins]]\n|  location =London\n| isbn =0-00-255563-8\n| year =1996\n|postscript=<!--None-->}}.\n* {{Citation\n| last =S\u00fcss\n| first =Joachim\n| title =Bhagwans Erbe: Die Osho-Bewegung heute\n| publisher =Claudius Verlag\n|  location =Munich\n| isbn 